}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-frwlucs","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-frwlucs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-unwo9kv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-unwo9kv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-r2htctq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r2htctq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"直接写出来的人可以理解的数据，在java中叫做字面量"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-51sbqy9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-51sbqy9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-yelwa42","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yelwa42","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举例：“HelloWorld”，666，13.14"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o05q02x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o05q02x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那Java中有哪些类型的字面量呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2vk7uw9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2vk7uw9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/a3df9e257b6c4e6a97344e8d9f82d11d.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wtfe3j1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wtfe3j1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了Java中的字面量后，下面我们到IDEA中去演示一下字面量的使用："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cjuka4p","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cjuka4p","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n        字符串字面量：        用双引号括起来的内容。\"HelloWorld\",\"黑马程序员\"\n        整数字面量：        不带小数的数字。666,-88\n        小数字面量：        带小数的数字。13.14,-5.21\n        字符字面量：        用单引号括起来的内容。'A','0','我'\n        布尔字面量：        布尔值，表示真假。true,false\n */\npublic class LiteralDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //字符串字面量\n        System.out.println(\"HelloWorld\");\n        System.out.println(\"黑马程序员\");\n\n        //整数字面量\n        System.out.println(666);\n        System.out.println(-88);\n\n        //小数字面量\n        System.out.println(13.14);\n        System.out.println(-5.21);\n\n        //字符字面量\n        System.out.println('A');\n        System.out.println('0');\n        System.out.println('我');\n\n        //布尔字面量\n        System.out.println(true);\n        System.out.println(false);\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cp6ru1n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cp6ru1n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"讲解完毕之后，大家赶快动手练习一下吧。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c31hzr4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c31hzr4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2 数据类型"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-93qjvk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-93qjvk8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"刚才我们学习了字面量，而Java是一种强类型语言，针对每种数据都给出了明确的数据类型，那我们刚才学习的几种字面量分别应该是什么类型的呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jh63dxe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jh63dxe","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/7eb01f78f8084b78939bbede8b5d9123.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-s7cgbla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s7cgbla","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那为什么会有不同的数据类型呢？因为"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3j1dqed","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3j1dqed","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-k4nmzmr","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k4nmzmr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-waj9sym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-waj9sym","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不同的数据类型分配了不同的内存空间"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sml8gyn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sml8gyn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ecpi30v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ecpi30v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不同的内存空间，所存储的数据大小是不一样的"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-syen11j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-syen11j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在讲解不同的数据类型前，这里我们先普及一个小知识，就是字节的概念："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ig9z5y2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ig9z5y2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计算机中存储数据的最小单位是：字节(byte)，用B表示。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-x3rz4rm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x3rz4rm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以看一下硬盘存储的文件：以字节为单位"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fqt50ly","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fqt50ly","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/1055e439868a41748e5c864f20a6cef1.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ulf6vy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ulf6vy4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了帮助大家更好的理解字节这个单位，我们来说一下，常见的存储单位："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zs4ubda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zs4ubda","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1TB = 1024GB"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lxue9d6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lxue9d6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1GB = 1024MB"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xr1amad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xr1amad","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1MB = 1024KB"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3dokgsu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3dokgsu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1KB = 1024B"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4azef5p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4azef5p","updated":"2026030