"这样就太麻烦了，那么，有没有一种流程语句，能够简化这种操作呢？答案肯定是有的，就是我们的循环结构，它就可以通过一个比较简单的结构来控制我们的手机展示1000次。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hyajofn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hyajofn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如说，带着这样写就可以了，这就是循环结构。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-heba949","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-heba949","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/b42d93240a474bfb97accd817f70fe23.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-a2zg3oj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a2zg3oj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解完毕之后，我们来说一下这一节的安排："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-68icjm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-68icjm0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/38f69b279abc44e884ec85dca2b4a50e.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i0fxdkm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i0fxdkm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来学习顺序结构"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-esgdnbj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-esgdnbj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.1 顺序结构"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-02nokqr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Prope