图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/6f86d5411923462bab88c306e5c63770.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fkd06gd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fkd06gd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⑤ 如何删除断点"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-al7hlel","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-al7hlel","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择要删除的断点，单击鼠标左键即可。也就是把第一步的动作，再做一次即可。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6f5r36v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6f5r36v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结一下，Debug的使用流程："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sr1iftl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sr1iftl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"①如何加断点：选择要设置断点的代码行，在行号的区域后面单击鼠标左键即可\n\n②如何运行加了断点的程序：在代码区域右键Debug执行\n\n③看哪里：看Debugger窗口，看Console窗口\n\n④点哪里：点(Step Over F8) 开始，点(Stop)结束\n\n⑤如何删除断点：选择要删除的断点，单击鼠标左键即可\n123456789\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-62sp056","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-62sp056","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过Debug的方式看一下，如下代码的执行流程："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f805r9u","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f805r9u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    Debug查看程序执行流程\n */\npublic class DebugDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义一个int类型的变量，用来表示价格\n        int price = 998;\n\n        //输出变量\n        System.out.println(price);\n\n        //修改变量的值\n        price = 888;\n\n        //再次输出变量的值\n        System.out.println(price);\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-blm0637","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-blm0637","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3 选择语句之if"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ht03o7b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ht03o7b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择语句有两种结构："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-uuggy45","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-uuggy45","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-vvye8y4","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vvye8y4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-lnq1uu6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lnq1uu6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"if语句"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-754s82u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-754s82u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-io49xxn","Type":