pe":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tdvh3lk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解完if语句格式1之后，下面我们到IDEA中去使用一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-a2x4dn6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a2x4dn6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    if语句格式1\n */\npublic class IfDemo01 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义一个变量，用来表示绿灯的状态\n        boolean isGreen = true;\n        isGreen = false;\n\n        if(isGreen) {\n            System.out.println(\"绿灯行\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q1mqckc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q1mqckc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.2 if语句格式2和格式3"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hb5z236","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hb5z236","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"刚才我们通过if语句格式1进行了判断，是绿灯的时候，可以通行，但是不是绿灯的时候，没有告诉我不可以通行啊。所以，这里就产生了if语句的第二种格式，先在代码中演示，再回去总结："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hwqf068","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hwqf068","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    if语句格式2\n */\npublic class IfDemo02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义一个变量，用来表示绿灯的状态\n        boolean isGreen = true;\n        isGreen = false;\n\n        if (isGreen) {\n            System.out.println(\"绿灯行\");\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(\"不是绿灯，不允许行使\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-g45ob47","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g45ob47","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"演示完毕后，我们来说一下，if语句格式2："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-gdwsqi5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gdwsqi5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w5e8q20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w5e8q20","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/9d0a004972e147058a0c5ac64c648c45.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xfr88oh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xfr88oh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"范例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nhnmr8k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nhnmr8k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/64b8258f12e543a3b6080524d10dc9d4.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tsn8wyl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tsn8wyl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"执行流程："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hwyu957","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hwyu957","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/2f4b095f2a044fbaa0169411aaa88381.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rq8l97z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rq8l97z","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"讲解完if语句格式2之后，我们到IDEA中再去看一段代码："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qzlay0s","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qzlay0s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class IfDemo03 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义三个变量，表示交通信号灯的三种状态\n        boolean isRed = true;\n        boolean isGreen = true;\n        boolean isYellow = true;\n        \n        if (isRed) {\n            System.out.println(\"红灯停\");\n        }\n\n        if (isGreen) {\n            System.out.println(\"绿灯行\");\n        }\n\n        if (isYellow) {\n            System.out.println(\"黄灯亮了等一等\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314151617181920\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-axunm1u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-axunm1u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很明显，这是不合理的，因为我们把三种状态都设置为true了，而实际生活中，只会有一种状态为true，怎么解决呢多种情况的判断呢？这个时候就产生了if语句的第三种格式，先在代码中演示，再回去总结："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-547lznl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-547lznl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    if语句格式3\n */\npublic class IfDemo03 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义三个变量，表示交通信号灯的三种状态\n        boolean isRed = true;\n        boolean isGreen = true;\n        boolean isYellow = true;\n\n        //红灯\n//        isGreen = false;\n//        isYellow = false;\n\n        //绿灯\n//        isRed = false;\n//        isYellow = false;\n\n        //黄灯\n//        isRed = false;\n//        isGreen = false;\n\n        //出现了故障，信号灯都不亮了\n        isRed = false;\n        isGreen = false;\n        isYellow = false;\n\n        if(isRed) {\n            System.out.println(\"红灯停\");\n        }else if(isGreen) {\n            System.out.println(\"绿灯行\");\n        }else if(isYellow) {\n            System.out.println(\"黄灯亮了等一等\");\n        } else  {\n            System.out.println(\"交通信号灯故障，请在保证安全的情况下通行\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233343536373839\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-eolu3ji","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-eolu3ji","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"演示完毕后，我们来说一下，if语句格式3："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-peipmn6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-peipmn6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"if语句格式3："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6hvt2vy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6hvt2vy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ect1qsy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ect1qsy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/d18972c8a510496a8942b337f536f671.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tgfxern","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tgfxern","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"执行流程："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7lszfii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7lszfii","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/dcd669e20a4746408c9be10b572ca787.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4x9ll3v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4x9ll3v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.3 案例1(交通信号灯)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bwcrcmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bwcrcmz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：交通信号灯由红灯、绿灯、黄灯组成，请通过程序实现不同的信号灯给出不同的提示。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-033hvq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-033hvq5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提示信息：红灯停、绿灯行、黄灯亮了等一等"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n6new06","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n6new06","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/025a46f71378475caa7696bcf671091e.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5ke0qwr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5ke0qwr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7ej2nl3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7ej2nl3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fdqqbtr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fdqqbtr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 用哪种类型来表示信号灯的三种状态呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-729q0fn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-729q0fn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用int类型来表示信号灯的三种状态(1表示红灯，2表示绿灯，3表示黄灯)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8dp43sw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8dp43sw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 用if语句的哪种格式来实现该需求呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kfa1fys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kfa1fys","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般来说：1种情况的判断用if格式1,2种情况的判断用if格式2，多种情况的判断用if格式3"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-llxi804","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-llxi804","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ if语句判断的表达式该怎么写呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n9qbi1h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n9qbi1h","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"int light = 1;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tx3pd64","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tx3pd64","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"if(light == 1) {…}"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vkac8t5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vkac8t5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"="}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"=：是关系运算符，用来判断两个数据是否相等，如果相等，结果为true，否则为false"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tbvlhwi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tbvlhwi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕后，我们来说一下实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ndto23i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ndto23i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5nj0r60","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5nj0r60","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个int类型的变量用来表示信号灯的状态(1表示红灯，2表示绿灯，3表示黄灯)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7mzvonw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7mzvonw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 用if语句格式3进行多种情况的判断"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sshctel","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sshctel","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 根据不同的情况给出不同的提示信息"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8cdkpxj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8cdkpxj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了实现步骤，下面我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-se2ktzg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-se2ktzg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：交通信号灯由红灯、绿灯、黄灯组成，请通过程序实现不同的信号灯给出不同的提示。\n    提示信息：红灯停、绿灯行、黄灯亮了等一等\n */\npublic class IfTest01 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //1:定义一个int类型的变量用来表示信号灯的状态(1表示红灯，2表示绿灯，3表示黄灯)\n        int light = 1;\n        light = 2;\n        light = 3;\n        light = 4;\n\n        //2:用if语句格式3进行多种情况的判断\n        //3:根据不同的情况给出不同的提示信息\n        if (light == 1) {\n            System.out.println(\"红灯停\");\n        } else if (light == 2) {\n            System.out.println(\"绿灯行\");\n        } else if (light == 3) {\n            System.out.println(\"黄灯亮了等一等\");\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(\"交通信号灯故障，请在保证安全的情况下通行\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122232425\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-88wjgn7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-88wjgn7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.4 关系运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-olyx7gm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-olyx7gm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java中的关系运算符有如下几种："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xg5rm0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xg5rm0k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/1f74541e999a4f4a8bb4af6778e12c14.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8na2vuq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8na2vuq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解了Java中的关系运算符之后，下面我们到IDEA中去使用一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3eg49f7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3eg49f7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    关系运算符\n */\npublic class OperatorDemo01 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义三个int类型的变量\n        int i = 10;\n        int j = 20;\n        int k = 10;\n\n        //等于：==\n        System.out.println(i == j);//false\n        System.out.println(i == k);//true\n        System.out.println(\"--------\");\n\n        //不等于：!=\n        System.out.println(i != j);//true\n        System.out.println(i != k);//false\n        System.out.println(\"--------\");\n\n        //大于：\u003e\n        System.out.println(i \u003e j);//false\n        System.out.println(i \u003e k);//false\n        System.out.println(\"--------\");\n\n        //大于等于：\u003e=\n        System.out.println(i \u003e= j);//false\n        System.out.println(i \u003e= k);//true\n        System.out.println(\"--------\");\n\n        //千万不要把==写成了=\n        System.out.println(i = j); //20\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2kskvqh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2kskvqh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后，我们来总结一下，刚才在演示代码的时候有两个注意事项："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-egw0g24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-egw0g24","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/fb3d7863e62643fe91f787bd6fc72ba7.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w2wwpj2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w2wwpj2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.5 案例2(奇偶数)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-crrohmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-crrohmz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：给定一个整数，请用程序实现判断该整数是奇数还是偶数，并在控制台输出该整数是奇数还是偶数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3g7qb2n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3g7qb2n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提示：偶数是能够被2整除的整数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9gv87hz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9gv87hz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1ozt56u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1ozt56u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xql6piw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xql6piw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 如何判断一个整数是奇数还是偶数？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pcj2d9c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pcj2d9c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"整数对2进行取余，余数为0是偶数，否则为奇数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0y7a91s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0y7a91s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 用if语句的哪种格式来实现该需求呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-plyuy1u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-plyuy1u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该整数要么是偶数，要么是奇数，2种情况，所以用if语句格式2"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-92lt28s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-92lt28s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕后，我们来说一下实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9289uew","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9289uew","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-d5ao96u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d5ao96u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个int类型的整数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p33u041","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p33u041","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 用if语句格式2进行判断"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fsj8c20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fsj8c20","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 根据是否是偶数给出不同的提示信息"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-gfcfoiq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gfcfoiq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了实现步骤，下面我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-gzrcrcp","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gzrcrcp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：给定一个整数，请用程序实现判断该整数是奇数还是偶数，并在控制台输出该整数是奇数还是偶数\n */\npublic class IfTest02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //1:定义一个int类型的整数\n        int number = 10;\n        number = 9;\n\n        //2:用if语句格式2进行判断\n        //3:根据是否是偶数给出不同的提示信息\n        if (number % 2 == 0) {\n            System.out.println(number + \"是偶数\");\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(number + \"是奇数\");\n        }\n        \n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2ssp5wc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2ssp5wc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.6 案例3(手机以旧换新)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w48e3de","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w48e3de","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：张三想买一台7988元的新手机，他的旧手机在二手市场能卖1500元，而手机专卖店推出以旧换新优惠，把他旧手机交给店家，新手机就能够打8折优惠。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-afgnf73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-afgnf73","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了更省钱，要不要以旧换新？请通过程序告诉张三"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-a435s6x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a435s6x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xgmtxc6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xgmtxc6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qwvhj73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qwvhj73","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 计算不使用以旧换新的花费"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dgiyhpc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dgiyhpc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7988 - 1500"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q8u0zcq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q8u0zcq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 计算使用以旧换新的花费"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bk5ftc1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bk5ftc1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7988 "},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 0.8"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xnioin7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xnioin7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 用if语句的哪种格式来实现该需求呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5dajneg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5dajneg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"if语句格式2"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-juy9z3t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-juy9z3t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕后，我们来说一下实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ioojgnu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ioojgnu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4vrczrc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4vrczrc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义变量(money1)纪录不使用以旧换新的花费"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vwsglyk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vwsglyk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 定义变量(money2)纪录使用以旧换新的花费"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ucksrp9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ucksrp9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 用if语句格式2进行判断 money1是否大于money2"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4z3rn35","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4z3rn35","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④ 根据判断结果，给出相应的提示"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5kt8qi7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5kt8qi7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了实现步骤，下面我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1rlok86","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1rlok86","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：张三想买一台7988元的新手机，他的旧手机在二手市场能卖1500元，而手机专卖店推出以旧换新优惠，\n        把他的旧手机交给店家，新手机就能够打8折优惠。为了更省钱，要不要以旧换新？请通过程序告诉张三\n */\npublic class IfTest03 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //1:定义变量(money1)纪录不使用以旧换新的花费\n        int money1 = 7988 - 1500;\n\n        //2:定义变量(money2)纪录使用以旧换新的花费\n        double money2 = 7988 * 0.8;\n\n        //3:用if语句格式2进行判断 money1是否大于money2\n        //4:根据判断结果，给出相应的提示\n        if (money1 \u003e money2) {\n            System.out.println(\"使用以旧换新更省钱\");\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(\"不使用以旧换新更省钱\");\n        }\n        \n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-t71iwqe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-t71iwqe","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.7 案例4(你是青年人吗)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-48vlr4p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-48vlr4p","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：给出你的年龄，通过程序判断你是否属于青年人？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7c7r6jn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7c7r6jn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提示：世界卫生组织，经过对全球人体素质和平均寿命进行测定，对年龄划分标准作出了新的规定"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xh739ub","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xh739ub","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/bb32cf9a90484c3e82c9f0cac236a6f2.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5kebohj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5kebohj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wrfybob","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wrfybob","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rh36o1t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rh36o1t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 如何判断一个年龄是否属于青年人？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6w31ort","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6w31ort","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"年龄要大于等于18，并且小于等于65"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6osucpi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6osucpi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 在Java中如何表示并且的关系呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-l9fyxr0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l9fyxr0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"age \u003e=18 \u0026\u0026 age\u003c=65"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-m3hnsq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-m3hnsq5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026amp;\u0026amp; ：是逻辑运算符，用来连接两个结果为boolean类型的表达式，都为true，结果为true，否则为false"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0d1v8ys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0d1v8ys","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕后，我们来说一下实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zxbjt5j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zxbjt5j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现步骤："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5mg2qhj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5mg2qhj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个int类型的变量来表示你的年龄"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-j6i6jib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-j6i6jib","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 用if语句格式2进行判断看你是否属于青年人"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fpo23e0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fpo23e0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 根据是否是青年人给出不同的提示信息"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-akeopbc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-akeopbc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了实现步骤，下面我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sfwkw0j","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sfwkw0j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：给出你的年龄，通过程序判断你是否属于青年人？\n    提示：青年人的年龄范围 18~65\n */\npublic class IfTest04 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //1:定义一个int类型的变量来表示你的年龄\n        int age = 22;\n        age = 100;\n\n        //2:用if语句格式2进行判断看你是否属于青年人\n        //3:根据是否是青年人给出不同的提示信息\n        if(age\u003e=18 \u0026\u0026 age\u003c=65) {\n            System.out.println(\"你是青年人\");\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(\"你不是青年人\");\n        }\n        \n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314151617181920\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nfuc2z2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nfuc2z2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.8 逻辑运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9nlc8kd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9nlc8kd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Java中常用的逻辑运算符有如下几种："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w9tun1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w9tun1c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/303dc035c2e4465b8a9c11840020fc29.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sa7037w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sa7037w","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解了Java中的逻辑运算符之后，下面我们到IDEA中去使用一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n717krw","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n717krw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    逻辑运算符\n */\npublic class OperatorDemo02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义变量\n        int i = 10;\n        int j = 20;\n        int k = 30;\n\n        //逻辑与：\u0026\u0026\n        System.out.println((i\u003ej) \u0026\u0026 (i\u003ek));//false \u0026\u0026 false\n        System.out.println((i\u003cj) \u0026\u0026 (i\u003ek));//true \u0026\u0026 false\n        System.out.println((i\u003ej) \u0026\u0026 (i\u003ck));//false \u0026\u0026 true\n        System.out.println((i\u003cj) \u0026\u0026 (i\u003ck));//true \u0026\u0026 true\n        System.out.println(\"-----------------------\");\n\n        //逻辑或：||\n        System.out.println((i\u003ej) || (i\u003ek));//false || false\n        System.out.println((i\u003cj) || (i\u003ek));//true || false\n        System.out.println((i\u003ej) || (i\u003ck));//false || true\n        System.out.println((i\u003cj) || (i\u003ck));//true || true\n        System.out.println(\"-----------------------\");\n\n        //逻辑非：!\n        System.out.println(!(i\u003ej));//!false\n        System.out.println(!!(i\u003ej));//!!false\n        System.out.println(!!!(i\u003ej));//!!!false\n        System.out.println(!!!!(i\u003ej));//!!!!false\n        \n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c7vu5fl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c7vu5fl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.9 三元运算符"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4iz9q6l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4iz9q6l","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来学习三元运算符："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yhlu697","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yhlu697","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：关系表达式 ？表达式1 ：表达式2；"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i56syax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i56syax","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"范例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：a \u003e b? a: b;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c9nqdkt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c9nqdkt","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"执行流程："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zrvux9e","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zrvux9e","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-3t92abo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3t92abo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-s6vzxep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s6vzxep","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先计算关系表达式的值"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-x8fr309","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x8fr309","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-8s6h08n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8s6h08n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果值为true，表达式1的值就是运算结果"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果值为false，表达式2的值就是运算结果"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cnyftw0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cnyftw0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"了解了三元运算符的执行流程后，下面我们到IDEA中去使用一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o6cu9oy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o6cu9oy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    三元运算符\n */\npublic class OperatorDemo03 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        int a = 10;\n        int b = 20;\n\n        int max = a \u003e b ? a : b;\n\n        System.out.println(\"较大的值是：\" + max);\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nxkivj8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nxkivj8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"##### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.3.10 三元运算符和if语句格式2的区别"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7iebij7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7iebij7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里呢，我们来讲解一下三元运算符和if语句格式2的区别，它们有什么区别呢？我们先到IDEA中进行讲解，然后再回来总结："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-85y4j3t","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-85y4j3t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    三元运算符和if语句格式2的区别\n */\npublic class OperatorTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义两个int类型的变量\n        int a = 10;\n        int b = 20;\n\n        //需求：获取两个数中的较大值\n        //if语句实现\n//        int max;\n//        if (a \u003e b) {\n//            max = a;\n//        } else {\n//            max = b;\n//        }\n//        System.out.println(\"较大的值是：\" + max);\n\n        if(a \u003e b) {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的值是：\" + a);\n        }else {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的值是：\" + b);\n        }\n\n        //三元运算符实现\n        int max = a \u003e b? a: b;\n        System.out.println(\"较大的值是：\" + max);\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-n0voggo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-n0voggo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"讲解完毕之后，回来总结一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7hb5ikn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7hb5ikn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ostk4nq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ostk4nq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5uojym4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5uojym4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果if语句控制的内容：是用变量纪录数据值，可以通过三元运算符改进"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dnvs89g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dnvs89g","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/faa2d333b5b842ff9e1093b79a719715.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kmzlr6r","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletCha