,"updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-eosb136","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-eosb136","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意观察方法的出现和消失，以及变量的变化"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kjivfhd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kjivfhd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.4 练习1(输出较大值)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-230io16","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-230io16","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：设计一个方法用于打印两个数中的较大数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ef05re5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ef05re5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-le9rh8n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-le9rh8n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sslxg4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sslxg4b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cm72e8q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cm72e8q","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 方法中定义两个变量，用于保存两个数字"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kkrmihu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kkrmihu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-l9n5c49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l9n5c49","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④ 在main()方法中调用定义好的方法"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wl7l5ap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wl7l5ap","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕之后，我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c2pk8ol","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c2pk8ol","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：设计一个方法用于打印两个数中的较大数\n\n    分析：\n        1:定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n        2:方法中定义两个变量，用于保存两个数字\n        3:使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        4:在main()方法中调用定义好的方法\n */\npublic class MethodTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //在main()方法中调用定义好的方法\n        getMax();\n    }\n\n    //定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n    public static void getMax() {\n        //方法中定义两个变量，用于保存两个数字\n        int a = 10;\n        int b = 20;\n\n        //使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        if(a \u003e= b) {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的数是：\" + a);\n        } else {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的数是：\" + b);\n        }\n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-f1y8u64","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-f1y8u64","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.5 带参数方法的定义和调用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nfaqee5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nfaqee5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面呢我们来学习带参数方法的定义和调用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5ny5rrk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5ny5rrk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-m2zagyp","Type":"NodeP