ated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：设计一个方法用于打印两个数中的较大数，数据来自于方法参数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fq6ja9b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fq6ja9b","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pwichdc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pwichdc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lnwz0ci","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lnwz0ci","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9ubve1w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9ubve1w","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 为方法定义两个参数，用于接收两个数字"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wkw2eax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wkw2eax","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mzmxn8x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mzmxn8x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④ 在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用字面量）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hpgc2cf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hpgc2cf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⑤ 在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用变量）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-idnkyxw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-idnkyxw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕之后，我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-czjhkxo","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-czjhkxo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：设计一个方法用于打印两个数中的较大数，数据来自于方法参数\n\n    分析：\n        1:定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n        2:为方法定义两个参数，用于接收两个数字\n        3:使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        4:在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用字面量）\n        5:在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用变量）\n */\npublic class MethodTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用字面量）\n        getMax(10,20);\n//        getMax(a:10,b:20); //idea的智能提示，不要手动的去写a,b\n//        getMax(30);\n//        getMax(10.0,20,0);\n        //调用方法的时候，人家要几个，你就给几个，人家要什么类型，你就给什么类型\n\n        //在main()方法中调用定义好的方法（使用变量）\n//        int a = 10;\n//        int b = 20;\n//        getMax(a,b);\n        int x = 10;\n        int y = 20;\n        getMax(x,y);\n    }\n\n    //定义一个方法，用于打印两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n    //为方法定义两个参数，用于接收两个数字\n    public static void getMax(int a, int b) {\n        //使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        if(a \u003e= b) {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的数是：\" + a);\n        }else {\n            System.out.println(\"较大的数是：\" + b);\n        }\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233343536373839\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hciv9tj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hciv9tj","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.8 带返回值方法的定义和调用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hxud6pk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hxud6pk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面呢我们来学习带返回值方法的定义和调用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-slhmy5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-slhmy5c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-88i55qg","Type":"N