"Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xg52xse","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4v6bf56","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4v6bf56","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-7j0x8f9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7j0x8f9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法定义时return后面的返回值与方法定义上的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数据类型要匹配"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，否则程序将报错"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0n4qf8u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0n4qf8u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了带返回值方法的定义格式后，我们到IDEA中去演示一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q5a41xl","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q5a41xl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    带返回值方法的定义和调用\n\n    定义格式：\n        public static 数据类型 方法名(参数) {\n           return 数据;\n       }\n */\npublic class MethodDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n//        isEvenNumber(10);\n//        //true;\n\n        boolean flag = isEvenNumber(10);\n        //boolean flag = true;\n        System.out.println(flag);\n\n//        if(flag) {\n//            System.out.println(\"是偶数就输出这句话\");\n//        }\n    }\n\n    //需求：定义一个方法，该方法接收一个参数，判断该数据是否是偶数，并返回真假值\n    public static boolean isEvenNumber(int number) {\n        if (number % 2 == 0) {\n            return true;\n        } else {\n            return false;\n        }\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ko0q6bl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ko0q6bl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"演示完毕之后，回到资料我们总结一下带返回值方法的调用和注意事项："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-digo6jw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-digo6jw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-eddlo0m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-eddlo0m","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/920a0f2552ac489c8f8cfcbb0a430d06.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-v9h8xrw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-v9h8xrw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/71320e68348e450aaf3320969c721ec8.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9ruc7mx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9ruc7mx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意事项："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1cbf8xc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1cbf8xc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-bb5h2fi","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bb5h2fi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1icjyq4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1icjyq4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法的返回值 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"通常会使用变量接收"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，否则该返回值将无意义"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pze90a6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pze90a6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.9 练习3(输出较大值)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-huj6cja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-huj6cja","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：设计一个方法可以获取两个数的较大值，数据来自于参数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qe8pjgb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qe8pjgb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dehiihx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dehiihx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fvex84e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fvex84e","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 定义一个方法，用于获取两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-g18spj1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g18spj1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"② 使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kw7llkp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kw7llkp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③ 根据题设分别设置两种情况下对应的返回结果"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8eerbqn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8eerbqn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④ 在main()方法中调用定义好的方法并使用变量保存"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-19033s4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-19033s4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分析完毕之后，我们到IDEA中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4xd4n3q","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4xd4n3q","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：设计一个方法可以获取两个数的较大值，数据来自于参数\n\n    分析：\n        1:定义一个方法，用于获取两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n        2:使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        3:根据题设分别设置两种情况下对应的返回结果\n        4:在main()方法中调用定义好的方法并使用变量保存\n */\npublic class MethodTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //在main()方法中调用定义好的方法并使用变量保存\n//        int max = getMax(10,20);\n//        System.out.println(max);\n\n        int max = getMax(10, 20); //.var的使用，它能够帮我们自动补齐左边的内容\n        System.out.println(max); //max.sout，能够把max变量放到输出语句中\n\n        System.out.println(getMax(10,20));\n        System.out.println(getMax(10, 20));\n    }\n\n    //定义一个方法，用于获取两个数字中的较大数，例如：getMax()\n    public static int getMax(int a,int b) {\n        //使用if语句对两个数字的大小关系进行处理\n        //根据题设分别设置两种情况下对应的返回结果\n        if(a \u003e= b) {\n            return a;\n        } else {\n            return b;\n        }\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bm035i5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bm035i5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.10 方法的注意事项"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-x5adb75","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x5adb75","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来说一下方法的注意事项，讲解注意事项，是为了让我们以后能够避免类似的问题，这里呢我们讲解两个注意事项："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-04bftxe","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-04bftxe","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-te9xwli","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-te9xwli","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-emiaaz9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-emiaaz9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法不能嵌套定义"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/1553bfc905364f01ae953e62bad4c6af.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vq206xg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vq206xg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1e3y4m5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1e3y4m5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"void表示无返回值，可以省略return，也可以单独的书写return，后面不加数据"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/03a8f472181447ab8e7c33671a20c29a.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hc5zmrw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hc5zmrw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"讲解完毕后，到IDEA中去演示一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-l38aozo","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l38aozo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    方法注意事项：\n        方法不能嵌套定义\n        void表示无返回值，可以省略return，也可以单独的书写return，后面不加数据\n */\npublic class MethodDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n\n    }\n\n    public static void methodOne() {\n        return;\n    }\n\n    public static void methodTwo() {\n//        return 100;\n\n        return;\n\n//        System.out.println(\"HelloWorld\");\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ihazxfv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ihazxfv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"到此，方法的注意事项，我们就讲解完毕了。大家了解即可，自己定义方法的时候，注意就好。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-h9zhw9t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h9zhw9t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11：方法的通用格式"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dzws6p1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dzws6p1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11.1 方法通用格式"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-amchnms","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-amchnms","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前面呢，我们讲解了方法定义的多种格式，其实呢，方法定义只有一种格式，这里我们来看一下方法定义的通用格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vjt1341","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vjt1341","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-23hmti6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-23hmti6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/243ff0f66ad74ccb9cd7fa65fbebcaf4.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fcjcqzr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fcjcqzr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"格式说明："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-y7jbbr9","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-y7jbbr9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ao1x9pa","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ao1x9pa","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-i9uiqai","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i9uiqai","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"public static 修饰符，目前先记住这个格式"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rnmd1wh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rnmd1wh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5m77aff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5m77aff","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"返回值类型 方法操作完毕之后返回的数据的数据类型，如果方法操作完毕，没有数据返回，这里写void，而且方法体中一般不写return"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hmb970d","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hmb970d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-l1wdrgr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-l1wdrgr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法名 调用方法时候使用的标识"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qri7537","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qri7537","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-tcq2fev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tcq2fev","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"参数 由数据类型和变量名组成，多个参数之间用逗号隔开"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6yl1xyh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6yl1xyh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-hs6099v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hs6099v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法体 完成功能的代码块"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-uxt37w7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-uxt37w7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-tgqi38n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tgqi38n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"return 如果方法操作完毕，有数据返回，用于把数据返回给调用者"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cdglp2f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cdglp2f","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在我们就知道了一个完整的方法格式了，那后续我们在自己编写方法的时候，如何正确的编写一个方法呢？这里给大家说一个小技巧："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-axwla4t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-axwla4t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"定义方法时，要做到 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"两个明确"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p550xzr","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p550xzr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-86yt2i3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-86yt2i3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-qna7qys","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qna7qys","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明确返回值类型： 主要是明确方法操作完毕之后是否有数据返回，如果没有，写void；如果有，写对应的数据类型"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lwvk1qo","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lwvk1qo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-czyrwph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-czyrwph","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"明确参数： 主要是明确参数的类型和数量"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i08zbzs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i08zbzs","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而在调用方法时，我们要知道下面两种不同返回值类型的方法调用："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kua6o8y","Type":"NodeList","ListData"