lockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：设计一个方法用于比较两个整数是否相等，调用方法，把结果在控制台输出。\n */\npublic class MethodTest02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        boolean flag = compare(10, 20);\n        System.out.println(\"10和20相等吗：\" + flag);\n\n        flag = compare(10,10);\n        System.out.println(\"10和10相等吗：\" + flag);\n    }\n\n    /*\n        使用两个明确分析该方法的参数和返回值\n        参数：int a,int b\n        返回值类型：boolean\n     */\n    public static boolean compare(int a,int b) {\n        //比较两个整数是否相等\n//        if(a == b) {\n//            return true;\n//        } else {\n//            return false;\n//        }\n\n//        boolean flag = (a == b) ? true : false;\n//        return flag;\n\n//        boolean flag = (a == b);\n//        return flag;\n\n        return a == b;\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122232425262728293031323334\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-z5gle8i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-z5gle8i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11.4 练习3(较大值)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rjuzavz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rjuzavz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：设计一个方法用于获取三个整数较大值，调用方法，把结果在控制台输出。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zz95ra6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zz95ra6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来简单的分析一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5yszs5y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5yszs5y","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分析："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rftrkrq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rftrkrq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"① 方法定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-z4b1yay","Type":"NodeCode