ode","Data":"/*\n    需求：设计一个方法用于判断一个整数是否是水仙花数，调用方法，把结果在控制台输出。\n */\npublic class MethodTest04 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n//        boolean flag = isFlower(111);\n//        System.out.println(flag);\n//\n//        flag = isFlower(153);\n//        System.out.println(flag);\n\n        for (int i=100; i\u003c1000; i++) {\n            //i\n//            boolean flag = isFlower(i);\n//            if(flag) {\n//                System.out.println(i);\n//            }\n            if(isFlower(i)) {\n                System.out.println(i);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    /*\n       使用两个明确分析该方法的参数和返回值\n        参数：int number\n        返回值类型：boolean\n     */\n    public static boolean isFlower(int number) {\n        //判断一个整数是否是水仙花数\n        int ge = number % 10;\n        int shi = number / 10 % 10;\n        int bai = number / 100 % 10;\n\n        if ((ge * ge * ge + shi * shi * shi + bai * bai * bai) == number) {\n            return true;\n        } else {\n            return false;\n        }\n    }\n}\n1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132333435363738394041\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yvkq83v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yvkq83v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12：方法重载"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lr9fa7a","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lr9fa7a","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12.1 方法重载"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-obivxve","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-obivxve","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们学习方法中一个非常重要的特性：方法重载。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6xspkb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6xspkb7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，我们来说一下，什么是方法重载。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dgathmc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dgathmc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法重载："},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指同一个类中定义的多个方法之间的关系，满足下列条件的多个方法相互构成重载"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-x9kwvp5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-x9kwvp5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-excy79a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-excy79a","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-a8hxq2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-a8hxq2j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多个方法在同一个类中"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-r258h0a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r258h0a","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-fnbkkya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fnbkkya","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多个方法具有相同的方法名"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vyecc0n","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vyecc0n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-jft8xg4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jft8xg4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多个方法的参数不相同，类型不同或者数量不同"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kp9jjy2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kp9jjy2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如下图："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-s0mbx3s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-s0mbx3s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/65ac9147f95c46fdb4a88f63fcd46ed8.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-r2gpyuu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r2gpyuu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了什么是方法重载后，我们来说一下 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法重载的特点："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-uqpugsd","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-uqpugsd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1xolka2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1xolka2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-45juq5r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-45juq5r","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型不同或者数量不同重载仅对应方法的定义，与方法的调用无关，调用方式参照标准格式"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8jz9qlp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8jz9qlp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-i2s393i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i2s393i","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重载仅针对同一个类中方法的名称与参数进行识别，与返回值无关，换句话说不能通过返回值来判定两个方法是否相互构成重载"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qb423pz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qb423pz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如下图："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-z1dl7fb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-z1dl7fb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"在这里插入图片描述"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/b6d172fe86d64b17a64348af8aa368f0.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-11xejrp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-11xejrp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了方法重载及其特点后，我们到IDEA中去体验一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-r2qewo7","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-r2qewo7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    方法重载：\n        多个方法在同一个类中\n        多个方法具有相同的方法名\n        多个方法的参数不相同，类型不同或者数量不同\n\n        调用方法的时候，Java虚拟机会通过参数的不同来区分同名的方法\n */\npublic class MethodDemo {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //调用方法\n        int result = sum(10, 20);\n        System.out.println(result);\n\n        double result2 = sum(10.0, 20.0);\n        System.out.println(result2);\n\n        int result3 = sum(10, 20, 30);\n        System.out.println(result3);\n    }\n\n    //需求1：求两个int类型数据和的方法\n    public static int sum(int a,int b) {\n        return a + b;\n    }\n\n    //需求2：求两个double类型数据和的方法\n    public static double sum(double a,double b) {\n        return a + b;\n    }\n\n    //需求3：求三个int类型数据和的方法\n    public static int sum(int a,int b,int c) {\n        return a + b + c;\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233343536\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2r7udo5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2r7udo5","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12.2 练习(比较相等)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-hesxnbc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-hesxnbc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：使用方法重载的思想，设计比较两个整数是否相等的方法，兼容全整数类型（byte,short,int,long）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ympgec9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ympgec9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比较整数是否想等，前面我们已经做过了，这里只不过是写几个重载的方法而已，基本思路讲解过了，这里就不在讲解了，我们直接到idea中去实现"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kqwqdo4","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kqwqdo4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    需求：使用方法重载的思想，设计比较两个整数是否相等的方法，兼容全整数类型（byte,short,int,long）\n */\npublic class MethodTest {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        System.out.println(compare(10,20));\n        System.out.println(compare((byte) 10,(byte) 20));\n        System.out.println(compare((short) 10,(short) 20));\n        System.out.println(compare(10L,20L));\n    }\n\n    //int\n    public static boolean compare(int a,int b) {\n        System.out.println(\"int\");\n        return a == b;\n    }\n\n    //byte\n    public static boolean compare(byte a,byte b) {\n        System.out.println(\"byte\");\n        return a == b;\n    }\n\n    //short\n    public static boolean compare(short a,short b) {\n        System.out.println(\"short\");\n        return a == b;\n    }\n\n    //long\n    public static boolean compare(long a,long b) {\n        System.out.println(\"long\");\n        return a == b;\n    }\n\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233343536\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ivzlmd8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ivzlmd8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"六、数组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fuk2am7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fuk2am7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本节目标："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-45me0nt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-45me0nt","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1thnxr3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1thnxr3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ykgqz84","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ykgqz84","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能够知道数组的作用"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6wf8t2n","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6wf8t2n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-kz23p7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kz23p7v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能够根据需求完成数组的定义和初始化"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-qcj0rq6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-qcj0rq6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-9lztfrn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9lztfrn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能够使用数组完成授课案例"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vdf99np","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vdf99np","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-33xmx7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-33xmx7x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能够理解数组内存图"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-d8nu8nr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d8nu8nr","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13：一维数组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8xiyec7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8xiyec7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13.1 数组概述和课程安排"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-m3zny72","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-m3zny72","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来学习数组。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8dd2kgh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8dd2kgh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那什么是数组呢？为了帮助大家理解，这里我们来看这样的一个场景："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rkciuw2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rkciuw2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/f84c4606ada9411d914b47bd7eb37a1d.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nrx5quz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nrx5quz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看这里，有一个学员的考试成绩，为了存储这个学员的考试成绩，我们可以采用一个变量进行存储。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2jsqy59","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2jsqy59","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是，假如这里有很多个学员的考试成绩，我们要存储该怎么办呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-wfni5zi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-wfni5zi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/f0e6f3a94270403caf212bdd77d5da2f.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8dug792","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8dug792","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"估计有同学就想到了，采用多个变量存储不就行了吗。对，想的没错。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jlohi5s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jlohi5s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"确实可以采用多个变量进行存储，只不过将来要对这多个变量进行操作就比较麻烦了，"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1pkbb83","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1pkbb83","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如说：找到成绩最高的学员。按照我们学过的获取两个数的较大值，需要编写大量的判断逻辑才能完成这个操作。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-b2yciwo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b2yciwo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很明显，采用多个变量存储不是好的解决方案。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lzmsgo4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lzmsgo4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那怎么办呢？我们再来回顾一下，目前出现的问题是："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2suo3ux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2suo3ux","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1：一次性声明大量的用于存储数据的变量，"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-88rifyq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-88rifyq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2：要存储的数据通常都是同类型数据，例如：考试成绩。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nzthebi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nzthebi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了解决这种大量的同类型的数据存储，Java就提供了数组供我们使用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bflyf47","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bflyf47","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如说：下面这种格式，就是定义了一个存储多个考试成绩的数组。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-rjf26ei","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rjf26ei","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-q5cyoni","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q5cyoni","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4cckt6k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4cckt6k","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"int"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"]"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" scores = {100,100,100,100,100,100,100…};"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vfo01y6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vfo01y6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对比一下，比定义多个变量要方便多了，而且操作起来也是很方便的，至于怎么操作，一会我们详细讲解。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3t239zz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3t239zz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好了，知道了数组可以解决这种问题后，我们给数组下一个定义："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kteln7v","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kteln7v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-1rjboga","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1rjboga","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-gl4oga7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gl4oga7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组(array)："},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"*"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是一种用于存储 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多个相同数据类型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的存储模型(可以理解为容器)。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-w6oz4ig","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-w6oz4ig","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了什么是数组后，我们来说一下数组这一节的安排："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ts791ev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ts791ev","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"Node