Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组遍历通用格式："},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"for (int i = 0; i \u003c scores.length; i++) {"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"scores"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"["}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"i"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBackslashContent","Data":"]"}]},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"}"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意：数组遍历指的是把数组中的元素取出来，取出来之后可以(打印，求和，判断…)。"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择哪种操作，得根据我们的实际需求来看。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-g4u8lw9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g4u8lw9","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好了，关于数组常见操作之遍历我们就先讲到这里"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-t75ip6d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-t75ip6d","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13.5 案例2(数组常见操作之获取最大值)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vpx4eru","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vpx4eru","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来学习数组中获取最大值："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8kczb3u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8kczb3u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而在讲解具体的实现之前，我们先通过一个场景，让大家对最值有一个认知："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dudlbyv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dudlbyv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看这里，这是一组家庭成员："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-aojcl3t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-aojcl3t","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/5c78cc437f2b4469a4c2ccc580182be4.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i300c88","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i300c88","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"给出一组数据，这些数据表示的是他们的年龄。68是最大年龄，4是最小年龄，所以，68和4就可以被称之为最值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lfoeuxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lfoeuxd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/20dc66cd3ea34010921ac10f783d4125.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ys693cq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ys693cq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再给出一组数据，这些数据表示的是他们的身高，171是最高身高，81是最低身高，所以，171和81就可以被称之为最值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-2rpwr9n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-2rpwr9n","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/1a8a48b62c2347c98919b9039e62fea5.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k5f0jmo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k5f0jmo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那这里的171为什么就是最高身高呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-iksvmdk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-iksvmdk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很明显，要想说171是最高身高，我们就要把这些数据从头到尾比较了一遍，最终找到了最高身高171。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-y4rdf6v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-y4rdf6v","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而要进行比较，我们的先把这些数据保存起来。这里我们就采用数组把这些数据给保存起来。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-t0h2zmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-t0h2zmz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"知道了大量同类型数据用数组保存和最值的知识后，我们来看一下我们的需求："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xqgboi7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xqgboi7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5dqo8gb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5dqo8gb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-fhhkpwx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fhhkpwx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我这里有一个数组，我现在要获取数组中的最大值"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cif4o59","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cif4o59","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/393d26275de349e09da9458378a75f3c.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-d44nqhk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d44nqhk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何实现呢？接下来，我们说一下思路："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3rfo460","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3rfo460","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1：因为我们最终，要得到最大值，所以，这里我们定义一个变量，用于保存最大值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lxg0ncn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lxg0ncn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是，它没有初始值，给多少比较合适呢？我总不能拿数组以外的数据进来吧，因为我们最终获取的是数组中的最大值。所以，我们就要从数组中找一个值作为初始值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0qdhftx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0qdhftx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般来说，我们取数组中第一个元素作为参照值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kdg1oqx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kdg1oqx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2：这样我们的最大值变量就有初始值了，接下来，我们与数组中剩余的数据逐个比较，比完之后，max中最终保存的是最大值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-i890nkp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-i890nkp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个动作怎么实现呢？我们来说一下：获取索引1-4，为什么不从0开始呢？因为0索引位置的值已经作为初始值了。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-jrcnjl3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-jrcnjl3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3：我们每次比较，需要把最大值保存到max变量中，这个动作，我们可以通过if语句实现。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bsim7rw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bsim7rw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4：当循环结束后，打印max变量就可以了，这个max里面保存的就是最大值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fbhe0px","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fbhe0px","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说完了数组获取最大值的思路后，我们到idea中去实现一下："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vv4x3hd","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vv4x3hd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    获取最大值\n */\npublic class ArrayTest02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        //定义数组\n        int[] arr = {12, 45, 98, 73, 60};\n\n        //定义变量max存储最大值，取第一个数据为变量的初始值\n        int max = arr[0];\n\n        //与数组中剩余数据逐个比对，每次比对将最大值保存到变量max中\n        for (int i=1; i\u003carr.length; i++) {\n            if(arr[i] \u003e max) {\n                max = arr[i];\n            }\n        }\n\n        //循环结束后输出变量max的值\n        System.out.println(\"max:\" + max);\n    }\n}\n12345678910111213141516171819202122\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-03l7izm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-03l7izm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13.6 案例3(数组常见操作之元素打乱)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kiuyu96","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kiuyu96","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来学习数组中元素打乱。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pd6v85y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pd6v85y","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那什么是元素打乱呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mbbj7hx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mbbj7hx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4c6xjvk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4c6xjvk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-28uwqsh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-28uwqsh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"元素打乱就是把数组中的元素随机交换位置，每次运行都可能产生不一样的结果"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p8uprde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p8uprde","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如： "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"arr"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"="},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":" {12, 45, 98, 73, 60};"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-d2qegqq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-d2qegqq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"遍历："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q7fiy59","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q7fiy59","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-gclkrlp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gclkrlp","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5mrq4cn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5mrq4cn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"正常情况下：12,45,98,73,60"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ulruone","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ulruone","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-4u5atr7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4u5atr7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"元素打乱后：45,73,12,60,98"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9r808ln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9r808ln","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"涉及到的操作："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-sar5o2l","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-sar5o2l","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-3byz37u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3byz37u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-9xwavdw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9xwavdw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"获取数组中元素的随机索引"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-k2w1qpw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-k2w1qpw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-6i5zy74","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6i5zy74","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-64k919z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-64k919z","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Random r = new Random();"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pf79h8u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pf79h8u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-5l6hb4s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5l6hb4s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"int index = r.nextInt(arr.length);"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-nsqr5hq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-nsqr5hq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-13x9m75","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-13x9m75","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数组中元素交换"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pgn8350","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pgn8350","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"获取随机索引比较好实现，但是元素交换该如何实现呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-u3eeynf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-u3eeynf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里为了帮助大家更好的理解，我们给出这样的一个场景来理解数据交换："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-cbk40bw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cbk40bw","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把啤酒杯和红酒杯里面的酒进行交换"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q4cf678","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q4cf678","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/91a3c78156454752ab9420e81dbece20.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-p2ijh4h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p2ijh4h","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何实现呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-o8jekru","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-o8jekru","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一步：找来一个同类型的空酒杯"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yotz71s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yotz71s","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/557dfee01f204073bce725bf70fa