CodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-rmiqrkq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"/*\n    数组使用中的两个小问题\n        1：索引越界：访问了数组中不存在的索引对应的元素，造成索引越界问题\n            ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException\n\n        2：空指针异常：对象不再指向堆内存，还想继续访问数据，访问失败\n            NullPointerException\n\n        null：空值，引用数据类型的默认值，表示不指向任何有效对象\n */\npublic class ArrayTest02 {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        int[] arr = new int[3];\n        //输出元素\n        //Exception in thread \"main\" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: Index 3 out of bounds for length 3\n//        System.out.println(arr[3]);\n        System.out.println(arr[2]);\n\n        //把null赋值给arr\n        arr = null;\n        //输出元素\n        //Exception in thread \"main\" java.lang.NullPointerException: Cannot load from int array because \"arr\" is null\n        if(arr != null) {\n            System.out.println(arr[0]);\n        }\n    }\n}\n123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ey553bo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ey553bo","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于仅仅是验证讲解的结论，故不需要练习。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-g9v1ngh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g9v1ngh","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14：二维数组"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-gx2r2yu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gx2r2yu","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14.1 二维数组概述和课程安排"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-bqyecy7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-bqyecy7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来学习二维数组。前面我们讲解的数组，一般称之为一维数组。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-kdop0o7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kdop0o7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了帮助大家理解二维数组呢？这里我们来看这样的一个场景："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-u1j2vxn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-u1j2vxn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求：我们要存储多个班级的学生的考试成绩，该怎么办呢？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ozeyw2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ozeyw2w","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果要存储一个班级中多个学生的考试成绩，我们就可以采用数组来存储。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-fns5mt0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-fns5mt0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在的问题是？多个班级的考试成绩，我们针对每个班级都采用数组存储。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3n44ek2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3n44ek2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一个班级：数组1"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-q1hb89j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-q1hb89j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二个班级：数组2"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-b3j6hgv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-b3j6hgv","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三个班级：数组3"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"…"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-anhprqz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-anhprqz","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但是多个班级，也可以采用数组存储啊。所以，Java就提供了二维数组供我们使用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-ol6x75j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ol6x75j","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"No