","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6t12koy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第一个地方：看类所在的包"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pvzxc09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pvzxc09","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"("},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/direct/a2ed5ecdffc34420a87521145659a62b.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-mdci0nq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-mdci0nq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么要看这里呢，因为java.lang包下的类，我们是可以直接使用的，不需要导包。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9a8surc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9a8surc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其他包下的类，我们都是要导包后才能使用的，至于如何导包，下个知识我们会讲解。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vcxg3hy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vcxg3hy","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"很明显，String类在使用的时候，我们是不需要导包的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1hba5pd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1hba5pd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第二个地方：看类的描述"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-gfcofja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-gfcofja","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是看这里，这里一般描述了类是干什么的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4yoqeon","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4yoqeon","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"["},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":